Program: Outlook
Title: Ecuador Coup
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbqzz
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
Antonio Vargas talks about the coup in Ecuador which was a joint operation by military and indigenous people. Also, conductor Loris Tjeknavorian of Armenian Philharmonic Orchestra talks about defying political chaos and an earthquake, and women who think submission to their husband makes for a good marriage. Show less